<H3> <TI>   Official on Deputies' Refusal To Vote on Constitution </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  WS2802105694 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 0400 
GMT 28 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS2802105694 </F>
