<F P=100> Turkey </F>
<H3> <TI>   Explosions Damage Recruiting Office, NAP Office </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2801175294 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1600 
GMT 28 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2801175294 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of regional map] </F>
  [Text] Four persons were slightly injured when terrorists 
bombed a recruiting office and the Nationalist Action Party 
[NAP] provincial headquarters in Igdir. 
  According to information obtained from Igdir Governor 
Semsettin Uzun, a group of terrorists threw a bomb at the 
recruiting office and escaped around 1330. The explosion 
damaged the building. 
  Meanwhile, at around the same time, a bomb thrown at the NAP 
provincial headquarters exploded on the ground, where it fell 
after hitting the balcony. Four passersby were slightly 
injured. Operations are under way in the region to catch the 
terrorists. 

</TEXT>

