<H3> <TI>   Explosion Damages Democracy Party Office in Ankara </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA3001161894 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1520 GMT 30 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA3001161894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ankara, Jan 30 (A.A) -- An explosion at the 
Democracy Party office of Mamak District of Ankara Province 
early Sunday [30 January] caused heavy damage, while no injuries 
were reported. 
  There were no immediate claims of responsibility for the 
attack which occurred in the outskirts of the capital. 
  On 20 January another office of the party also in Ankara was 
bombed. One person was injured in that attack. 

</TEXT>

