<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] A medium-strength tremor was felt in Malatya at 
around midday. According to information received from Kandilli 
Observatory at Bogazici University, the tremor registered 4.8 on 
the Richter scale. There was no loss of life or damage to 
property. 

