<H3> <TI>   Earthquake Causes Property Damage in Manisa </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2801174594 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 28 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2801174594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of regional map] </F>
  [Text] A medium-strength tremor was felt in Manisa and the 
surrounding area. There were shattered windows and cracked 
walls in several houses following the tremor. 
  According to information received from Kandilli Observatory 
at Bogazici University, the tremor occurred at 1745 [1545 GMT] 
and registered 5.0 on the Richter scale. The tremor was also 
felt in Izmir, Aydin, Balikesir, and Denizli. 

</TEXT>

