Drnovsek, and Israeli Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres separately. 
At the second meeting, Demirel and Peres discussed the latest 
stage in the Middle East peace process and the relations between 
Turkey and Israel. Peres said the development achieved in the 
relations between the two countries will further grow thanks to 
the sensitive attitude of the two sides, and this will help 
bring lasting peace to the Middle East. 

