Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Salzgitter (DPA) -- In Salzgitter this evening, at 
least two police officers were injured in a protest involving 
over 1,000 person demonstrating against an election campaign 
meeting by the right-wing extremist Republikaner. Several 
windows of a school assembly hall were also smashed. Eggs and 
